1008.name: Harrys's 1st Receipt
1008.description: A receipt Harrys received after ordering tools. Take this and go to Blacksmith Altran.

1009.name: Harrys's 2nd Receipt
1009.description: The receipt that Harrys has received after placing an order for his tools. Go and gather golem shards needed for creating the tool.

1010.name: Golem Shard
1010.description: Shards of rock that have fallen from the Golem's body. Gather 5 and take them to Blacksmith Altran.

1011.name: Tool Box
1011.description: A toolbox containing the tools that Blacksmith Altran has forged. Take this to Magister Harrys at the temple.

1012.name: Delivery List
1012.description: Take the heavy wooden box to Trader Jackson. The bolts of cloth to Trader Silvia. Take the clay pot to the warehouse keeper Rant.

1013.name: Heavy Wood Box
1013.description: The wooden box to be delivered to Trader Jackson of the weapons shop.

1014.name: Cloth Bundle
1014.description: Bolts of cloth that need to be delivered to Trader Silvia of the grocery store.

1015.name: Clay Pot
1015.description: The clay pot that must be delivered to the warehouse keeper Rant.

1016.name: Jackson's Receipt
1016.description: The receipt that Jackson has issued upon receiving his wooden box. Take this to Guard Arnold.

1017.name: Silvia's Receipt
1017.description: The receipt that Silvia has issued upon receiving her bolts of cloth. Take this to Guard Arnold.

1018.name: Rant's Receipt
1018.description: The receipt issued by Rant upon his receiving of the clay pot. Take this to Guard Arnold.

1019.name: Official Letter
1019.description: An official letter that the Lord of Gludio has sent to Sir Colin Windawood, calling a meeting. Deliver this to Sir Windawood.

1020.name: Flame Shard
1020.description: A fragment of soul ore of fire. Can be taken from the fire spirit salamander. Give it to Trader Katerina.

1021.name: Ice Shard
1021.description: A fragment of elemental stone of water. Can be taken from the water spirit undine. Give to Trader Katerina.

1022.name: Lilith's Letter
1022.description: A letter written by Lilith in longing for her lover, separated a thousand years ago. Find out news about her lover for her.

1023.name: Theon's Diary
1023.description: A diary written by Theon in longing for his lover, separated a thousand years ago. Take this to Lilith.

1024.name: Adamantite Ore
1024.description: Adamantite ore. All of it is imported from Gracia. Gather 20 of these and take them to Warehouse Keeper Wilford.

1025.name: Clay Tablet
1025.description: A tablet praising Beleth that the devil Nerkas possessed. Deliver this to High Priest Biotin.

1026.name: Silvery Spidersilk
1026.description: The spider silk of the silver spider. Take this to Trader Unoren of the weapons shop.

1027.name: Unoren's Receipt
1027.description: The receipt issued by the magic shop. Take this and go to Trader Creamees.

1028.name: Creamees's Ticket
1028.description: A ticket issued by the warehouse. Take this and go to Warehouse Keeper Julia.

1029.name: Nightshade Leaf
1029.description: The leaf of the nightshade plant. Take this to Nerupa.

1030.name: Cracked Skull
1030.description: The cracked skull of the Dark Horror. Take this to Magister Vlasty.

1031.name: Perfect Skull
1031.description: Skull of the dark horror. Take this to Magister Vlasty.

1032.name: Fox Fur
1032.description: A mane of keltirs. It is soft and luxurious, and used to spin thread and yarn. Take this to Cristel.

1033.name: Fox Fur Yarn
1033.description: Yarn spun out of the fur of keltirs. Take this to the former tailor Warehouse Keeper Rolfe, and he will make it into the doll's hair.

1034.name: Maiden Doll
1034.description: A doll resembling a Human maiden. Take this to Lighthouse Keeper Rockswell.

1035.name: Plague Dust
1035.description: A powder obtained from the plague zombie. Take this to Hierarch Asterios.

1036.name: Andellia's Letter
1036.description: A letter from Andellia asking her sister Thalia to send her the fruit of the Mother Tree.

1037.name: Fruit of the Mother Tree
1037.description: Fruit that the Mother Tree bears once every few years. Take this to Andellia.

1038.name: Rumiel's 1st Poem
1038.description: The scroll containing Rumiel Moonshine's first poem. Gather all four and take them to Sentinel Starden.

1039.name: Rumiel's 2nd Poem
1039.description: The scroll containing Rumiel Moonshine's second poem. Gather all four and take them to Sentinel Starden.

1040.name: Rumiel's 3rd Poem
1040.description: The scroll containing Rumiel Moonshine's third poem. Gather all four and take them to Sentinel Starden.

1041.name: Rumiel's 4th Poem
1041.description: The scroll containing Rumiel Moonshine's fourth poem. Gather all four and take them to Sentinel Starden.

1042.name: Wererat's Fang
1042.description: The fang of a dead ratman. Collect these to take to Master Ellenia.

1043.name: Varool Foulclaw's Fang
1043.description: The fang of Varool Foulclaw, leader of the ratmen. Take this to Master Ellenia.

1044.name: Kirunak Skull
1044.description: Kirunak's skull obtained after killing Kirunak, the leader of the drevanuls. Take this to Trader Creamees.

1045.name: Zombie's Skin
1045.description: A skin obtained from marshland zombies. Collect five and go to Trader Minaless.

1046.name: Nightmare Crystal
1046.description: A crystal used by the succubus Merkenis to cast nightmares. Take this to Tetrarch Vellior.

1048.name: Spellbook: Might
1048.description: Spellbook needed to learn Might. Used by Human Mystics, Elven Mystics and Dark Mystics. Required level: 7

1049.name: Spellbook: Ice Bolt
1049.description: Spellbook needed to learn Ice Bolt. Used by Human Mystics, Elven Mystics and Dark Mystics. Required level: 7

1050.name: Spellbook: Battle Heal
1050.description: Spellbook needed to learn Battle Heal. Used by Human Mystics, Elven Mystics and Dark Mystics. Required level: 14

1051.name: Spellbook: Vampiric Touch
1051.description: Spellbook needed to learn Vampiric Touch. Used by Human Mystics and Dark Mystics. Required level: 14

1052.name: Spellbook: Flame Strike
1052.description: Spellbook needed to learn Flame Strike. Used by Human Wizards, Elven Wizards and Dark Wizards. Required level: 20

1053.name: Spellbook: Cure Poison
1053.description: Spellbook needed to learn Cure Poison. Used by Human Mystics, Elven Mystics and Dark Mystics. Required level: 7

1054.name: Spellbook: Group Heal
1054.description: Spellbook needed to learn Group Heal. Used by Human Mystics, Elven Mystics and Dark Mystics. Required level: 14

1055.name: Spellbook: Curse: Poison
1055.description: Spellbook needed to learn Curse: Poison. Used by Human Mystics and Dark Mystics. Required level: 7

1056.name: Spellbook: Curse: Weakness
1056.description: Spellbook needed to learn Curse: Weakness. Used by Human Mystics and Elven Mystics. Required level: 14

1057.name: Spellbook: Summon Meal
1057.description: Spellbook needed to learn Summon Meal. Used by Human Mystics and Elven Mystics.

1058.name: Spellbook: Shield
1058.description: Spellbook needed to learn Shield. Used by Human Mystics, Elven Mystics and Dark Mystics. Required level: 7

1059.name: Spellbook: Know Enemy
1059.description: Spellbook needed to learn Know Enemy.

1060.name: Lesser Healing Potion
1060.description: A magical potion that slowly restores HP. Low endurance. Lesser Healing Potion

1061.name: Greater Healing Potion
1061.description: A magical potion that slowly restores HP. High endurance. Healing Potion

1062.name: Haste Potion
1062.description: A magical potion that increases speed.

1063.name: Tutorial Parchment
1063.description: Take the tutorial parchment to Grand Master Roien.

1064.name: Tutorial Parchment
1064.description: Take the tutorial parchment to Grand Master Roien.

1065.name: Tutorial Parchment
1065.description: Take the tutorial parchment to Nerupa.

1066.name: Tutorial Parchment
1066.description: Take the tutorial parchment to Mitraell, the chief of Dark Elves.

1067.name: Recommendation
1067.description: Take the recommendation to Grand Master Roien.

1068.name: Recommendation
1068.description: Take the recommendation to Grand Magister Gallint.

1069.name: Leaf of the Mother Tree
1069.description: Take the leaf of the Mother Tree to Nerupa.

1070.name: Blood of Mitraell
1070.description: Take the blood of Mitraell to Hierarch Mitraell.

1071.name: Hyacinth Charm
1071.description: A charm given by Hierarch Asterios. Go to the water source to seek those who pollute the waters of the Elven village.

1072.name: Hyacinth Charm
1072.description: A charm given by Hierarch Asterios. Go to the water source and obtain five handfuls of plague dust from the zombies.

1073.name: Beginner's Potion
1073.description: A magical potion that slowly restores HP. Low endurance. Lesser Healing Potion

1074.name: Boat Ticket: Talking Island to Gludin
1074.description: Boat Ticket: Depart Talking Island - Arrive Gludin Harbor

1075.name: Boat Ticket: Gludin to Talking Island
1075.description: Boat Ticket: Depart Gludin Harbor - Arrive Talking Island

1076.name: Carlon's Letter
1076.description: First half year financial summary of the Iron Gate Guild: balance sheet and profit and loss statement of the Dark Elven Village guild.

1077.name: Venom Sac
1077.description: A Giant Spider's Poison Sac of poisonous spider. Gather ten of these and take to Astaron.

1078.name: Wind Shard
1078.description: A fragment of the elemental stone of wind. You can get them from Lirein, the wind spirits. Collect these to take to Rizraell.

1079.name: Darin's Receipt
1079.description: A receipt for a magical potion Darin received after paying Baulro. This must be handed to Baulro.

1080.name: Baulro's Potion
1080.description: A potion of courage that Baulro has created for the shy Darin, but its effects are unknown. This must be delivered to Darin.

1081.name: Omen Beast's Eye
1081.description: The first of three materials Tetrarch Talloth asked you to collect.

1082.name: Taint Stone
1082.description: The second of three materials Tetrarch Talloth asked you to collect.

1083.name: Succubus Blood
1083.description: The third of three materials Tetrarch Talloth asked you to collect.

1084.name: Gludio Lord's Mark
1084.description: A mark indicating that the bearer is carrying out the orders of the lord. Keep this in your possession and hunt Orcs or werewolves.

1085.name: Orc's Necklace
1085.description: A bone necklace that Orc fighters possess on their bodies for magic purposes. Take this to Captain Gilbert.

1086.name: Werewolf's Fang
1086.description: Fangs from a dead werewolf. Take this to Captain Gilbert.

1087.name: Giant Spider's Leg
1087.description: The legs cut off from a giant spider. Collect 8 of these and take them to Alshupes.

1088.name: Undrias's Letter
1088.description: Abyssal Celebrant Undrias's letter. Take this letter to Trader Iria, Warehouse Keeper Dorankus, and Master Trudy.

1089.name: Ceremonial Dagger
1089.description: A ceremonial dagger used during the mass of darkness. Take this to Abyssal Celebrant Undrias.

1090.name: Dreviant Wine
1090.description: Holy wine used in the mass of darkness. Take this to Abyssal Celebrant Undrias.

1091.name: Garmiel's Scripture
1091.description: The scripture used during the mass of darkness. Take this to Abyssal Celebrant Undrias.

1092.name: Arujien's Letter
1092.description: The letter that Arujien has written in longing for Greenis. Show this to Gatekeeper Mirabel.

1093.name: Arujien's Letter
1093.description: The letter that Arujien has written in longing for Greenis. Show this to Trader Herbiel.

1094.name: Arujien's Letter
1094.description: Arujien's love letter. Since you have shown this to Mirabel and Herbiel, you must go back to Arujien.

1095.name: Spellbook: Attack Aura
1095.description: Spellbook needed to learn Attack Aura. Used by Elven Fighters and Dark Fighters. Required level: 10

1096.name: Spellbook: Elemental Heal
1096.description: Spellbook needed to learn Elemental Heal. Used by Elven Fighters. Required level: 15

1097.name: Spellbook: Drain Health
1097.description: Spellbook needed to learn Drain Health. Used by Knights and Dark Fighters. Required level: Dark Fighter - 15, Knight - 20

1098.name: Spellbook: Wind Walk
1098.description: Spellbook needed to learn Wind Walk. Used by Clerics, Elven Oracles and Shillien Oracles. Required level: 20

1099.name: Spellbook: Wind Shackle
1099.description: Spellbook needed to learn Wind Shackle. Used by Elven Mystics and Dark Mystics. Required level: 14
